---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="North Carolina Case Study | Upfront" description="See how Child Care Resources Inc. built an integrated statewide system with Upfront, redefining how North Carolina collects and manages child care data.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal hover:text-brand-teal/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        North Carolina
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-gray">
        Behind North Carolina's New Data Platform Powered by Upfront
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        As a lead agency for North Carolina's entire Child Care Resource & Referral (CCR&R) network, Child Care Resources Inc. (CCRI) supports families, providers, and regional partners in ways that go far beyond what appears on a website.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
        Together with Upfront, CCRI has built an integrated statewide system that redefines how child care data is collected, managed, and acted upon — connecting every piece of the ecosystem in one place.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- For Families -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        For Families
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Search, Connect, and Access Care in Minutes
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        CCRI's new public online search portal — <strong>FindChildcareNC.com</strong> — is the most comprehensive child care search in the state. Families can:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Filter by schedule, age, quality rating, pricing, languages, special needs, and more</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">View real-time vacancy data, so they're not calling closed or full programs</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Access the tool seamlessly from any device, with full mobile optimization and multilingual support</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Find results ranked for SEO to ensure every family searching online can discover it</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
        Behind the public search is a robust referral intake system used by family specialists statewide, allowing CCR&R staff to create referrals in minutes, manage family cases through a full call intake workflow, and view dashboards showing call volume, trends, and response rates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- For Providers -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-orange uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        For Providers
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Easy Account Management and Professional Growth
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        CCRI's work extends equally to supporting the providers who make North Carolina's early care and education system possible. The provider portal enables every licensed program to:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Quick Onboarding</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Claim and verify their account in less than two minutes
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Direct Updates</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Update data directly — from vacancies and pricing to hours and contact information — ensuring accuracy across the system
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-4">
        For Professional Development and Training, CCR&R teams can publish courses in a public catalog for providers to register through directly. Providers can pay online for training through a fully integrated payment system that automatically routes funds to the correct region.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
        The Technical Assistance and Coaching module gives CCR&R specialists the tools to quantify their impact with early educators, including configurable assessment templates and analytics showing where coaching efforts are most concentrated.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Data & Reporting -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        For All
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Real-Time Data and Reporting That Drives Change
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        Every module connects into a single data and reporting backbone. CCRI and regional partners can:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Run pre-built report templates or create custom self-service exports across families, providers, training, coaching, and referrals</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Access real-time supply and demand maps visualizing where care is available — and where it's not</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Analyze affordability deserts by viewing program costs as a percentage of median household income (MHI), revealing where child care is financially out of reach</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
          Why It Matters
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
          The launch of this statewide system is more than a technology upgrade — it's a rethinking of how North Carolina serves its families and early educators. From the first call a parent makes to the data driving state policy decisions, CCRI's infrastructure ensures that every interaction is informed, efficient, and equitable.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
